он Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Нотариус идорасининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#20} <span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-20 structure-20\" style=\"className:20 20; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#20}Ҳусусий нотариал <span class=\"leading\"></span>амалиёт билан шуғулланувчи нотариус</span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#20} </span><span class=\"structures structure-20 structure-4\" style=\"className:20 4; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#20}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#20}га</span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic; display: none;\">{#21}Давлат нотариал идорасининг рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-style: italic; display: none;\">{#19}-сон давлат нотариал идорасига</span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#19} </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 318.18282548476px;\">\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Аризачининг яшаш уйи рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-яшовчи </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">дан </span></p>\n<p></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">А<span class=\"leading\"></span>Р И З А</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси, </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Ариза санаси</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен – </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Аризачининг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> Ўзбекистон Республикаси «Нотариат тўғрисида»ги қонунининг 63-моддасига асосан, </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#22}Мол-мулк эгасининг вафот этган санаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">да вафот этган турмуш ўртоғим </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Вафот этган шахснинг Ф.И.О.си</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> билан биргаликда яшаб, никоҳимиз давомида орттирилган ва турмуш ўртоғим номига расмийлаштирилган умумий мол-мулкка, яъни </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#6}Аризачининг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Аризачининг яшаш уйи рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уй-жойнинг </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Улушнинг қисми</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> қисмига нисбатан мулк ҳуқуқи тўғрисида гувоҳнома беришингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Ариза берувчи: ____________________________________________________</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">Нотариуснинг</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-style: italic;\">тасдиқлов ёзуви</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 26.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p></p>\n</div></div>",
